Class FindAllBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xpert.faces.bean.FindAllBean

  • public abstract class FindAllBean
extends Object
    Generic bean to get objects, if is enum get values from enum, if is a entity try to select from data base. This bean works better on ViewScope to evict duplicates query.
